{
  "texts": [
    "With the rapid development of Neural Radiance Field (NeRF) [7,8,47,49,60,66], several works [28,36,51,52,65,72,73,77] also exploit NeRFs to model cars and static street backgrounds in outdoor environments.",
    "Moreover, notable examples like UniSim [77] and MARS [72] come equipped with a suite of scene-editing tools.",
    "However, these methods require extensive user involvement in intermediate editing steps and they fail to support external digital assets for data expansion.",
    "In this work, we proposeMethod Photorealistic Dim.",
